summary: Adds a tomb player home in riverwood.
descriptionHtml: [size=2]Have you wanted to live in a tomb? A dungeon? Like a draugur. Well with this mod it adds a little tomb with mannequins chests and crafting stations for every day needs. I has a nice comfy bed and a free armor piece. The tomb is in riverwood. It will already be on your map when you start up your game.[/size]
author: Seabatt
